        "text": "All authors should have received an author kit from Conference Publishing via e-mail by now. It contains instructions on how to submit the camera-ready version of your essay. \nOnward! Essays is looking for clear and compelling pieces of writing about topics important to the software community. An essay can be long or short. \nAn essay can be an exploration of the topic and its impact, or a story about the circumstances of its creation; it can present a personal view of what is, explore a terrain, or lead the reader in an act of discovery; it can be a philosophical digression or a deep analy ...",
