                "type": "text",
                "text": ": the Onward! paper by Weiher, Hirschfeld, and Taeumel looks aligned with your quest for moving  beyond function-based programming. And that reminds me that I have seen earlier work by Weiher on this topic, though I don't have concrete references at hand."
